    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project: Break//Down is a experimental 3D action-adventure brawler with a unique limb-based combat system. In this game you explore the EZON complex a mass production and distribution facility secretly gone rogue in the shoes of 2 fools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/4ac5fc28cdb8e888e36957a533b81e21.poster.avif?t=1771210444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/4ac5fc28cdb8e888e36957a533b81e21.webm?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/4ac5fc28cdb8e888e36957a533b81e21.mp4?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smash, Bash, and Mash your enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project: Break//Down utilises a unique physics based limb system where you can disable, dismantle and destroy your enemies, the limb system allows for dynamic flinch and ragdoll to allow for the satisfying feeling of weight and impact to every hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0b0af016eac2d24126f8e19d5ad155d4.poster.avif?t=1771210444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0b0af016eac2d24126f8e19d5ad155d4.webm?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0b0af016eac2d24126f8e19d5ad155d4.mp4?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Anything you can grab it a weapon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab anything in the environment you can get your hands on to dynamically change how you fight your enemies form; bottles, paint cans, an old pole, a plank of wood or even your foes limbs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/22e3d047c3fa3266b98c74c2a25209fa.poster.avif?t=1771210444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/22e3d047c3fa3266b98c74c2a25209fa.webm?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/22e3d047c3fa3266b98c74c2a25209fa.mp4?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Abuse the physics system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use physics and magnetic abilities to cause havoc and chaos for your foes in combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0c580a325dac1d03a62f5b1782d41d43.poster.avif?t=1771210444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0c580a325dac1d03a62f5b1782d41d43.webm?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/0c580a325dac1d03a62f5b1782d41d43.mp4?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the rogue EZON facility </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the facility after a secret robot revolution and discover the madness and shenanigans of the facility formed from laziness and incompetency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/81ee94416a4b5c3e0226cea72af3290b.poster.avif?t=1771210444\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/81ee94416a4b5c3e0226cea72af3290b.webm?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317220/extras/81ee94416a4b5c3e0226cea72af3290b.mp4?t=1771210444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
